data.description: Welcome to 1109 Miracle Drive! This inviting 3-bed, 2-bath home on just over an acre delights with its unique features. Upstairs, the lofted master suite is equipped with a jetted tub, a separate shower, and a generously sized walk-in closet.While the home requires some finishing touches to realize its full promise, its true appeal lies in the details. The property features a private, fenced yard, perfect for summer activities and gatherings. Inside, the wooden walls and flooring remind you of the cozy ambiance of a cabin retreat.This property also includes an additional dwelling unit that stands ready for transformation. Whether you envision a rec room, a private in-law suite, or extra storage space, the possibilities are vast! Contact us today to schedule a showing.
